parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I don’t see anything. What’s she going to show me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.What I am about to show you must remain a secret between us. Do you understand?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.The Storm on the Sea of Galilee, painted in 1633 and stolen by the Eclipse Guild in 1990.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoDe.How the hell did you find it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Careful, 1Hero. You’ve graduated to the next level…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlDe.Not everything we do is by the rules.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Doubtful. His plans were much larger. But with this painting, we have what we need to pin him on the theft.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.And just like that, the Guild is done and no one's the wiser that they’ve been operating here all along.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.A simple, easy to digest story. We’ll look like heroes and the city will go on like nothing ever happened.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Damn… We’re looking at a ten million dollar painting.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Your interview with Kimberly airs tonight. We will inform Channel 4 that we have the painting and soon you’ll reveal it to the public.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.We will let the story sit for a little while longer.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.We’re scratching Paul’s back, so he’ll continue to scratch ours.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.You’re going to leave the hunt for the painting in the news cycle while Duncan is still out there?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.We will keep a police presence at the church and the mansion. People will stay safe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.What’s Duncan’s ultimate plan? Why is he really here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.He’s here to take over where Charles left off.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.So Charles was the leader all along?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Since investigating his death. My team has gathered a lot of info that you’re not privy to.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Who all is on this team apart from Nellie? Are those treasure hunters on your team?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.The identities of the infiltrators will never be known to anyone but myself. It’s important…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’ll be honest with you, Andrea. I’m a nosy guy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.You’re a man whose potential has been squandered. I see it in you. I know you feel the same way.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.So this is it, then. This is how we operate.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.It should go without saying that not a word should be spoken about this painting until the time is right.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe.If any thief knew this was here, my life would be at risk.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.If Kimberly asks, tell her we’re still searching the mansion, but we’re positive it’s there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.They want this story. We’ll give them everything they need… Just not now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp.Enjoy your weekend, 1Hero. What’s left of it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl^.Holy shit. What have I gotten myself into?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp^.I want to climb the ladder, but this isn’t what I expected.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Damn. I’m looking at ten million dollars.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.This metal box is secured by a rusty lock and chain. Even if I had a key, it probably wouldn’t work.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaOp.My hacksaw isn’t strong enough to saw through this lock.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I can use my diamond saw to cut through the chain!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.We can’t find the comissioner. She’s disappeared.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.What’s up with this place? Where is Kimura living now?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’d like you to take inventory of what’s in this room… Need to make sure nothing goes missing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "OaBaEx.Yes, detective. There was some kind of Guild document I found.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.What kind of special code would young Kirk Chesterfield have used?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Nellie and Andrea probably wouldn’t know, since it was so long ago.");
